title: Psychic Warrior: The True Story of America's Foremost Psychic Spy and the Cover-Up of the CIA's Top-Secret Stargate Program
description: A highly decorated, exemplary Army officer, special operations infantryman, and an elite Airborne Ranger Company Commander describes his role as a member of a U.S. military intelligence agency that delved into the dark world of psychic espionage. Reprint.
author: David Morehouse
